Burundi Inflation Rate Rises to 11% in August on Food, Transport

-- B y   D e s i r e   N i m u b o n a
-- 
2011-09-22T07:33:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/burundi-inflation-rate-rises-to-11-in-august-on-food-transport.html
Inflation in Burundi accelerated to
11 percent in August as food and transport prices increased,
said Antoine Gahiru, a spokesman for the Burundian Institute of
Statistics and Economic Studies.  The inflation rate increased from 9.1 percent in July,
Gahiru said in an interview today in Bujumbura, the capital.
Prices climbed 1.4 percent in the month, he said.  Food costs increased 11 percent from a year earlier, while
transport surged 33 percent, Gahiru said. He didnâ€™t provide the
